@mnbbv: Well... when the rights (license) for HellGirl seasons 2 and 3 have been sold, specified was only right to produce Japanese audio - no dub.

That what you have watched on Animax Asia is probably their own dub, of Animax, and if no one have captured that specific airing, chance to get English dubbed version are slim to none.

However - even if that one is available - it would be encoded by me only in original language (in case of Dual audio) and eventually subs would be provided. Sorry, that's my policy.
